let us sing together the hymn,

180
00:16:02,837 --> 00:16:05,796
"O God, Our Help in Ages Past."

181
00:16:27,361 --> 00:16:29,227
<i>Let dogs delight to bark and bite,</i>

182
00:16:29,322 --> 00:16:31,279
<i>for God hath made them so.</i>

183
00:16:31,365 --> 00:16:33,402
<i>Let bears and lions growl and fight,</i>

184
00:16:33,493 --> 00:16:35,280
<i>for 'tis their nature too.</i>

185
00:16:35,369 --> 00:16:39,158
<i>But, ladies, you should never
