235
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:53,663
<i>Molly's reputation was destroyed,</i>

236
00:20:53,753 --> 00:20:56,871
<i>and Tom's heart was heavy with remorse.</i>

237
00:20:56,964 --> 00:20:59,126
<i>Perhaps Mr. Square had been right</i>

238
00:20:59,216 --> 00:21:03,210
<i>that the wicked are snared
in the work of their own hands.</i>

239
00:21:14,899 --> 00:21:17,232
Oh. Mr. Jones.

240
00:21:17,318 --> 00:21:20,311
- Where's Molly?
